n.笨蛋 【英】 n.笨蛋(a fool) 【考】 prudence : daredevil / sagacity : simpleton(蛮勇的人不会谨慎/ 傻瓜不会睿智) n. 笨蛋(在判断力或智力上有缺陷的人) 【记】简单的象一吨石头就是傻子. 【类】prudence: daredevil = sagacity: simpleton = constancy: turncoat = boor: sensitive蛮勇的人不会谨慎 = 傻瓜不会聪明 = 背叛者不会坚定 = 粗人不会敏感 【记】simple ton 一吨, 头脑简单象一吨铁一样 simpleton (n.)  1640s, probably a jocular formation from simple and -ton, suffix extracted from surnames. Compare skimmington, personification of an ill-used spouse, c.1600.
